*.pyc
# Fixture contamination from local analyze runs
tests/fixtures/*/.shipwright/
# Lockfiles generated inside adopt test fixtures by local uv runs
tests/fixtures/*/uv.lock
# The nested-shipwright fixture deliberately ships a shipwright_run_config.json
# as a nested-project detector marker. Re-include it past the repo-wide
# `shipwright_*_config.json` ignore so fresh clones / CI checkouts / iterate
# worktrees carry it — test_nested_project_detector needs it on disk.
!tests/fixtures/nested-shipwright/webui/shipwright_run_config.json
